title: American Horror Story Weekly Wednesday Live Stream
author: MaryGirl Moody
comment: The Apocalypse is that none of the actors can return and Ryan faces conflict when finding a new cast/plot

Ryan already confirmed Sarah is playing Cordelia and considering this is the Coven-Murder House crossover I think Sarah will be playing Cordelia and a new character. I'm new to your channel btw and I love it!
They just cast Michael Langdon.....Ahhhhhh!!!!!! So excited!!!

IN the same interview that Taissa said that she wasn't asked back, she also said that everyone in the cast is incredibly secretive and that Ryan won't let them spill anything. Perhaps Ryan is making the cast tell a bunch of lies in order to throw the whole fanbase for a loop.
The title of the first 2 episodes have just been released!!!!! (if you look up American Horror Story and go to episodes. episode 1 is called "The End" and episode 2 is called "The Morning After")
